### Starting Salary by Academic Field in Japan

| Field                        | Percentage of Total Enrollment | Starting Salary Range (¥ per year)  | Typical Range by Major                                                                                  |
|------------------------------|-------------------------------|-------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **Social Sciences**           | ~35-40%                       | ¥3.2 - ¥4.0 million                | Economics / Business Administration: ¥3.5 - ¥4.0 million <br> Law: ¥3.5 - ¥4.0 million <br> Political Science / International Relations: ¥3.2 - ¥3.7 million <br> Sociology / Psychology / Education: ¥3.0 - ¥3.4 million |
| **Humanities**                | ~15-20%                       | ¥2.8 - ¥3.5 million                | Literature / History / Philosophy: ¥2.8 - ¥3.2 million <br> Arts / Cultural Studies: ¥3.0 - ¥3.3 million <br> Linguistics: ¥3.2 - ¥3.5 million |
| **Natural Sciences**          | ~10-12%                       | ¥3.5 - ¥4.5 million                | Mathematics / Physics / Chemistry: ¥3.8 - ¥4.3 million <br> Biology / Earth Sciences: ¥3.5 - ¥4.0 million <br> Astronomy: ¥3.5 - ¥4.5 million |
| **Engineering**               | ~15-18%                       | ¥4.0 - ¥5.5 million                | Mechanical Engineering / Electrical Engineering: ¥4.0 - ¥4.5 million <br> Civil Engineering: ¥4.0 - ¥4.5 million <br> Chemical Engineering: ¥4.2 - ¥4.8 million <br> Computer Science / Information Engineering: ¥4.3 - ¥5.0 million <br> Environmental Engineering: ¥4.0 - ¥4.5 million <br> Aerospace Engineering: ¥4.5 - ¥5.5 million |
| **Medical & Health Sciences** | ~3-4%                         | ¥4.5 - ¥7.0 million                | Medicine: ¥6.0 - ¥7.0 million <br> Dentistry: ¥5.0 - ¥6.5 million <br> Pharmacy: ¥4.5 - ¥5.0 million <br> Nursing: ¥4.0 - ¥4.5 million <br> Public Health: ¥4.5 - ¥5.0 million |
| **Other Fields**              | ~5-10%                        | ¥2.8 - ¥4.2 million                | Agriculture / Veterinary Science: ¥3.0 - ¥3.5 million <br> Sports Science: ¥2.8 - ¥3.2 million <br> Design / Fine Arts: ¥3.0 - ¥3.5 million <br> Tourism and Hospitality: ¥3.2 - ¥4.0 million |
